msgid "  Everyone else is invited to listen in, either via the their own favourite client or via the [archive](https://botbot.me/freenode/fdroid-dev/) which updates in real time. Please be respectful of the fact that this is a meeting for actual contributors. See the bottom of this post for general questions and feedback.\n"
