#: _posts/2018-08-16-twif-17-the-reproducible-builds-and-encrypted-e-mail-edition.md
msgid "Everybody's favourite app, **[Easy xkcd](https://f-droid.org/packages/de.tap.easy_xkcd/)**, joins the list of apps sporting an [adaptive icon](https://developer.android.com/guide/practices/ui_guidelines/icon_design_adaptive). Other additions are a simplified Chinese translation, fixed What-if thumbnails, and Chrome Custom Tabs can now be disabled in the settings."
