msgid "[4.1.7 OTF-007 — Javascript Injection Into HTMLified Descriptions in Fdroidserver Metadata]({{ site.baseurl }}/docs/Second_Audit_Report/#f29-javascript-injection-into-htmlified-package-descriptions-in-fdroidserver-metadata-py)"
