#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2018-09-04-second-security-audit-results.md
msgid "The links are only displayed in the \"Links\" section.  Since there is a human review of those URLs, and those URLs are committed to git, we have left those to be open without validation. There are also other URLs like home page, issue tracker, etc.  I suppose we should show the full URL in the UI if they don't match a well known pattern.  Google Play also includes a link to a website that the app author provides."
